* Iron Raptor walked a little steadier towards Prowl now, seeing him get to 
his feet. She checked his mind a little when he comfirmed that he was 
alright, finding that he was gaining his energy back and getting stronger.
She, too, was beginning to get her strength back but much slower then 
Prowl.*

" I'm shaken up."

* She said to him once she was close enough that she didn't have to shout. 
Her systems were, just now, beginning to stabelize itself.
Seeing Prowl offer her an arm she took it, but hugged him instead of using 
him for support. But then she quickly leaned back.*

" Have you any idea of what you were doing?"

* It was a normal question, with no anger in it at all.*
